constituent: V.I.P., house, one, ceiling, few, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight
heisigStory: The V.I.P. indicated here is an important guest making a visit. The elements are: house . . . ceiling . . . few . . . shells.
hint: The V.I.P. visits your house, but your ceiling is too low for his inflated head, which he bumps and hurts. You have to give him your few shells as compensation.
koohiiStory1: This house is reserved to V.I.P. only. If you are not one of the few with enough money to call you that way, keep out!
